# Jira Operating Rules

- For each story: fetch acceptance criteria, post brief implementation plan, transition to In Progress with branch name, keep compliance comment before PR and after merge.
- Prefer highest-priority To Do; branch from `develop` with `feat/<JIRA-KEY>-<kebab-summary>`.
- Link PR in Jira; include issue key in branch and PR title.

MCP integration available; prefer MCP over raw API.
